    "how_to_apply": "\u003cp\u003eSend us an application to: \u003ca href=\"https://jobs.lever.co/Smile.io/9b8f234c-1686-4fb0-9708-ee1f1775fa86\"\u003ehttps://jobs.lever.co/Smile.io/9b8f234c-1686-4fb0-9708-ee1f1775fa86\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n",
